cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.RO 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.AI - The paper proposes a reinforcement learning approach to learn a single model for jointly reasoning about linguistic and visual input to execute instructions. 
2. cs.CL - The paper deals with natural language processing and understanding instructions given in text format. 
3. cs.LG - The paper uses a neural network agent to learn the mapping between instructions and visual observations to actions. 
4. cs.CV - The paper deals with visual observations and their mapping to actions. 
5. cs.RO - The paper evaluates the proposed approach in a simulated environment, which falls under the domain of robotics.
